  "format": "A live-to-tape watch-along of Christopher Nolan's 'The Dark Knight Rises.' Sean, Amanda, and Chris press play and talk through the trilogy-capper, from the plane hijacking cold open to the urine-powered climax, four days before the Oscars.",
  "segments": [
